Building Zoom

See doc/readme-qt.rst for instructions on building Zoom-Qt,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Zoom.

See doc/build-*.txt for instructions on building zoomd,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Zoom.

Further build information and documentation is available at
the official Zoom website, http://www.ZoomCoin.co
